WHAT IS IT?

PyroScope is a collection of tools for the BitTorrent protocol and especially the rTorrent client.

This is the core package and basic command line tools subproject.


INSTALLATION

On Ubuntu, do this:
    sudo aptitude install python-setuptools checkinstall
    sudo checkinstall easy_install pyrocore

See the http://code.google.com/p/pyroscope/wiki/QuickStartGuide for more.


